<h3>Welcome to TimeSink!</h3>

<p>Our goal is to become the premiere platform for discovering the freshest talent in cinema today. </p>

<p>We believe the viewer forms part of the creative act. Now you have the power to write reviews, share comments, upvote, and connect with other members around the world. </p>

<p> In addition to presenting <a href="www.timesinkpresents.com/films" style="text-decoration: none; color: black;"><u>films</u></a>, we also feature a blog section called <a href="www.timesinkpresents.com/blog" style="text-decoration: none; color: black;"><i><u>Tales from the Faucet</u></i> </a> where we'll regularly publish exclusive articles, interviews, and op-eds with a diverse range of topics and perspectives.</p>

