<h3>Filmmakers</h3>

<p>We don't discriminate between genre, duration, or budget. We are simply looking for films or series that impress us through storytelling, technique, and vision. Please consider <a href="www.timesinkpresents.com/submit" style="text-decoration: none; color: black;"><u>submitting</u></a> your film/series for a chance to be featured on TimeSink Presents.</p>

<p>Submissions include status updates so you'll know exactly when your film has been received, viewed, and judged.   </p>

<p>Each submission also comes with our written response. </p>

<p>Submissions are $25 each.</p>

